titleNullable: Water level of Kalu river at Rathnapura, Sri Lanka
subtitleNullable: Time Series data of water level of Kalu River at Rathnapura
descriptionNullable: This Data set consists of water level of Kalu River at Rathnapura, Sri Lanka from January 2020 to January 2021 at a sample period of 1 hour. Data set is suitable to predict the water level of Kalu river using as time series. The data set was obtained from the Irrigation Department of Sri Lanka.
